reviewText: Top notch comedy. Not like the dumbed down  nonsense on US TV

While Im waiting for my set to arrive I just want to say that this is one heck of a great show! It never stops being an enjoyable show, especially with Mark Heap as the creepy neighbor Jim.  *Edit* My set arrived finally in good shape, well packed, and Im looking forward to watching tonight!
Another fine entry in the FND series.
Shipped expeditiously and securely. Great show!!
